# Generated benchmark result dirs (bench/results/<date>-<sha>/). Ad-hoc local runs are
# ignored, but the README and committed baseline runs (the artifacts AC-G's "reproducible by a
# third party" criterion rests on) are kept — negate each committed run dir explicitly.
